## Balls, Inner Ring, Cage Disassembly Note  


1. Insert a screwdriver between the inner ring and cage to remove the balls.  

![](images/3.jpg)
  


USU31309  


2. Mark the inner ring and cage with paint. 
3. Turn the cage approximately \(30^{\circ}\) , then pull it away from the inner ring.  

![](images/4.jpg)
  


